er.", "Det er vanskelig \u00e5 stoppe urettferdig jobbing p\u00e5 kort sikt, s\u00e5 derfor kan man g\u00e5 til de bedriftene som markedsf\u00f8rer at de har gode arbeidsforhold og heller kj\u00f8pe kl\u00e6r fra dem.", "Christian (14)", "Vil du skrive til Snakk ut? Fyll inn skjema her , send leserinnlegget ditt p\u00e5 mail til snakkut@adresseavisen.no eller en SMS til 07200 med kodeord snakkut."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "meninger|snakkut"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a6ce935ab07d912cdac42a7f55eff6461f7ce389d2ec63ca920d345b1b3c1338"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-03-10T18:54:09.000Z"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/meninger/snakkut/article10383575.ece/cgkvar/ALTERNATES/w980-default/sp744756.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/00e1111540d1d4ea333bde034b3b7fde18e5f545.jpg?5892ef1d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Kl\u00e6r kan drepe -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "00e1111540d1d4ea333bde034b3b7fde18e5f545"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["meninger", "snakk ut", "leder"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "meninger,snakk ut,leder"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["meninger", "snakkut"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["tjene", "jobb", "billig arbeidskraft", "barn", "kl\u00e6r"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["snakk", "sweatshop"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "kambodsja"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["meninger", "meninger/snakkut"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/meninger/snakkut/article10383575.ece/cgkvar/ALTERNATES/w980-default/sp744756.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Kl\u00e